{"type":null,"faqId":49958,"title":"华为智能手表_如何调整表带长度？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body63898235\"><ul id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329088__ul27520356\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329088__li38213209\"><strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329088__b5698828165529\">不锈钢编织表带款：</strong>请根据您的手腕周长自行调整。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329088__li8262190\"><strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329088__b7250847\">真皮表带款：</strong>请优先根据您的手腕周长自行调整，若皮带上已有的扣孔无法满足您的舒适度，建议您前往当地专业机构（例如华为手表的零售商店或者传统手表店）进行调整。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329088__li65257631\"><strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329088__b49802935165521\">不锈钢链式表带款：</strong>调整链式表带需要特殊的工具，建议您前往当地专业机构（例如华为手表的零售商店或者传统手表店）进行调整。以避免自己手动调整时误操作而损坏手表表带。</li></ul></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":207,"faqType":"外观结构&配件","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022329088","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Appearance-Shell-Accessories","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448627734000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10","visitedTimes":119,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"调整,长度，表带","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}